            "name": "Monster Core pg. 343",
            "type": "link"
          },
          "name": "Monster Core",
          "page": 343,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "Giant wasps are much more dangerous but less common than their smaller kin, and\u2014to the relief of those who encounter them\u2014they tend to be solitary.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
